Class ReflectionHashCodeCacheKeyGenerator

All Implemented Interfaces:
CacheKeyGenerator<Long>
public class ReflectionHashCodeCacheKeyGenerator
extends HashCodeCacheKeyGenerator

An extension of HashCodeCacheKeyGenerator that uses reflection to generate hash codes for objects that don't implement hashCode. All of the same key uniqueness issues affect this generator as affect HashCodeCacheKeyGenerator

Pros Cons
Don't have to modify/implement argument object hashCode methods to get a non-colliding key generated. The slowest key generation strategy available due to use of reflection and complete object graph traversal.
